    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It's been a fantastic ride for me\u2014super reliable and still looking great! It\u2019s in really nice shape and ready to hit the road for many more adventures. If you're looking for a dependable set of wheels that's been well-loved and taken care of, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it!",
