    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a recently serviced VANOS system for precise variable valve timing. Power is delivered via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to the rear wheels through an M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis has undergone essential subframe reinforcement, and the suspension geometry remains true with crisp turn-in thanks to refreshed bushings. Recent Blackstone oil reports indicate healthy rod bearing wear. While the exterior shows minor road patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical vitals are robust, making this a technically sound example for the purist driver.",
